\c 6
\s UElisha wenza isimangaliso ngehloka
\p
\v 1 Amadodana abaprofethi asesithi kuElisha\x + 2.3.\x*: Khangela-ke, indawo esihlala kiyo lawe iminyene kakhulu kithi.
\v 2 Akusiyekele sihambe siye eJordani, sithathe khona, ngulowo lalowo isigodo esisodwa, sizenzele khona indawo yokuhlala kiyo. Wasesithi: Hambani.
\v 3 Omunye wasesithi: Akuvume, uhambe lenceku zakho. Wasesithi: Mina ngizahamba.
\v 4 Wasehamba labo; sebefikile eJordani bagamula izihlahla.
\v 5 Kodwa omunye esagamula ugodo, insimbi yawela emanzini. Wasememeza esithi: Maye, nkosi yami! Ngoba belebolekiwe\x + 4.3.\x*.
\v 6 Umuntu kaNkulunkulu wasesithi: Iwele ngaphi? Wasemtshengisa indawo. Wasegamula uswazi, wa\add lu\add*phosela khona, wenza insimbi yandenda\x + 2.21.\x*.
\v 7 Wasesithi: Zenyulele \add yona\add*. Waseselula isandla sakhe, wayithatha.
\s UElisha lebutho lamaSiriya
\p
\v 8 Kwathi inkosi yeSiriya isilwa loIsrayeli yacebisana lenceku zayo isithi: Ekuthanathaneni izakuba yinkamba yami.
\v 9 Umuntu kaNkulunkulu wasethumela enkosini yakoIsrayeli esithi: Qaphela ungedluli kulindawo, ngoba amaSiriya ehlele khona\x + 1 Kho. 20.7.\x*.
\v 10 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasithumela kuleyondawo umuntu kaNkulunkulu ayitshela yona wayixwayisa ngayo. Yasizilondoloza khona, kungekanye, njalo kungekabili\x + Eks. 18.20.\x*.
\v 11 Inhliziyo yenkosi yeSiriya yasikhathazeka kakhulu ngenxa yalinto. Yasibiza inceku zayo yathi kuzo: Kaliyikungitshela yini ukuthi ngubani kithi ongowenkosi yakoIsrayeli?
\v 12 Omunye wenceku zakhe wasesithi: Hatshi, nkosi yami, nkosi; kodwa uElisha umprofethi okoIsrayeli uyayitshela inkosi yakoIsrayeli amazwi owakhuluma phakathi kwekamelo lakho lokulala.
\v 13 Yasisithi: Hambani li\add ye\add*bona lapho akhona, ukuze ngithume ngimthathe. Wasetshelwa kwathiwa: Khangela, useDothani\x + Gen. 37.17.\x*.
\v 14 Yasithuma khona amabhiza lezinqola lebutho elinzima; basebefika ebusuku, bawuzingelezela umuzi.
\p
\v 15 Kwathi inceku yomuntu kaNkulunkulu isivukile ngovivi yaphuma, khangela-ke, ibutho lizingelezele umuzi kanye lamabhiza lezinqola. Inceku yakhe yasisithi kuye: Maye, nkosi yami! Sizakwenza njani?
\v 16 Wasesithi: Ungesabi, ngoba labo abalathi banengi okwedlula labo abalabo\x + 2 Lan. 32.7. Hlab. 55.18.\x*.
\v 17 UElisha wasekhuleka wathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, akuvule amehlo ayo ukuze ibone. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiwavula amehlo alelojaha, laselibona, khangela-ke, intaba igcwele amabhiza lenqola zomlilo zihanqe uElisha\x + 2.11. Hlab. 34.7. Zek. 1.8. 6.1-7.\x*.
\v 18 Sebehlele kuye, uElisha wakhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wathi: Akutshaye lababantu ngobuphofu\x + Gen. 19.11.\x*. Yasibatshaya ngobuphofu njengokwelizwi likaElisha.
\v 19 UElisha wasesithi kibo: Kayisiyo le indlela, futhi kayisiwo lo umuzi; ngilandelani, ngizalisa kulowomuntu elimdingayo. Kodwa wabasa eSamariya.
\p
\v 20 Kwasekusithi sebengene eSamariya, uElisha wathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, vula amehlo alaba ukuze babone. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasivula amehlo abo, basebebona; khangela-ke, babephakathi kweSamariya\x + 6.17.\x*.
\v 21 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuElisha ibabona: Baba, ngi\add ba\add*tshaye, ngi\add ba\add*tshaye yini\x + 8.9. 5.13.\x*?
\v 22 Wasesithi: Ungatshayi. Ungatshaya yini labo obathumbe ngenkemba yakho langedandili lakho\x + Gen. 48.22.\x*? Beka isinkwa lamanzi phambi kwabo ukuze badle banathe, baye enkosini yabo\x + Roma 12.20.\x*.
\v 23 Yasibalungisela idili elikhulu; sebedlile banatha, yabayekela bahamba, baya enkosini yabo. Ngakho amaviyo amaSiriya kawabesaphinda ukubuya elizweni lakoIsrayeli\x + 6.8,9. 5.2. 13.20. 24.2. 2 Lan. 22.1. 25.9,10,13. 26.11.\x*.
\s UElisha lokuvinjezelwa kweSamariya
\p
\v 24 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho uBenihadadi inkosi yeSiriya wabutha ibutho lakhe lonke, wenyuka wavimbezela iSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 20.2.\x*.
\v 25 Kwasekusiba lendlala enkulu eSamariya; khangela-ke, bayivimbela, kwaze kwathi inhloko kababhemi \add yathengiswa\add* nge\add nhlamvu\add* zesiliva ezingamatshumi ayisificaminwembili, lengxenye eyodwa kwezine yegajana lobudolilo bejuba nge\add nhlamvu\add* zesiliva ezinhlanu.
\v 26 Kwasekusithi inkosi yakoIsrayeli idlula phezu komduli, owesifazana wamemeza kiyo esithi: Siza, nkosi yami, nkosi!
\v 27 Yasisithi: \add Uba\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* ingakusizi, ngikusize ngokuvela ngaphi? Ebaleni lokubhulela kumbe esikhamelweni sewayini yini\x + Nani 18.27,30.\x*?
\v 28 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Ulani? Wasesithi: Lo owesifazana uthe: Letha indodana yakho ukuze siyidle lamuhla; kusasa-ke sizakudla indodana yami.
\v 29 Sasesiyipheka indodana yami, sayidla. Ngasengisithi kuye ngosuku olulandelayo: Letha indodana yakho ukuze siyidle. Kodwa wayifihla indodana yakhe\x + Dute. 28.53. Hez. 5.10.\x*.
\v 30 Kwasekusithi inkosi isizwa amazwi alowo owesifazana yadabula izigqoko zayo\x + 1 Kho. 21.27. Gen. 44.13.\x*. Yedlula phezu komduli; abantu basebebona, khangela-ke, kwakulesaka emzimbeni wayo, ngaphakathi\x + 1 Kho. 21.27. Gen. 44.13.\x*.
\v 31 Yasisithi: UNkulunkulu kenze njalo kimi langokunjalo engezelele, uba ikhanda likaElisha indodana kaShafati lizahlala kuye lamuhla\x + Ruthe 1.17.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa uElisha wayehlezi endlini yakhe labadala babehlezi laye\x + Hez. 8.1. 14.1. 20.1.\x*. \add Inkosi\add* yasithuma umuntu esuka phambi kwayo; isithunywa singakafiki kuye, yena wathi kubadala: Liyabona yini ukuthi indodana le yombulali ithume ukususa ikhanda lami\x + Isa. 1.21. 1 Kho. 18.4. 21.13.\x*? Bonani, lapho isithunywa sifika, livale umnyango, lisibandezele emnyango. Kakusizisinde zenkosi yaso yini emva kwaso\x + 7.17.\x*?
\v 33 Kwathi esakhuluma labo, khangela-ke, inkosi yehlela kuye, yathi: Khangela, lobububi buvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Ngingabe ngisayilindelelani iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Jobe 2.9.\x*?